title: (Wed Early Bird)  Bobby Talks About Co-Hosting The Today Show with Hoda + Mailbag: How To Not Invite Your Dad to Your Wedding + Bobby Feud: Top 10 Crossover Artists In Country Music
itunes:title: (Wed Early Bird)  Bobby Talks About Co-Hosting The Today Show with Hoda + Mailbag: How To Not Invite Your Dad to Your Wedding + Bobby Feud: Top 10 Crossover Artists In Country Music
description:
Bobby is co-hosting The Today Show with Hoda today and tomorrow! He tells us about his experience and shares some behind the scenes stories from The Today Show. Mailbag: A listener doesn't know the best way to tell her dad he's NOT invited to her wedding. We play the Bobby Feud and try to name the Top 10 country artists that crossovered to other music genres.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
